rComments: Good professor. Very kind and always willing to answer questions. Tries to make the class as engaging as possible!
Super engaged in class and always available to help you out! Really understanding and kind.

Jesse is a very good teacher!! Weither you speak English or French isn't a problem since he explains in both languages. I was a total beginner in Spanish so at first it looked hard but it was actually pretty easy, since the teacher and the TA are very good! The exams aren't too hard. If you wanna learn Spanish, take this class!!

Though I found the course to be rather hard at the end, the prof was amazing. Very caring and understanding, he'd answer every single one of our questions on zoom without getting frustrated (... and we had a lot). Overall super nice guy, makes Spanish fun to learn. Emailed him about a mistake on an exam and he fixed it no problem. + great TA
